      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a \"hum\" though... it feels like it's actually affecting how my brain works. like, the second that vibration starts, i can't think straight and i just get this intense, irrational rage. it feels intentional. like they know exactly what frequency does this. do you think there's any tech out there that could actually target someone's mood like that without being obvious?",
