    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it feels so deliberate. like, i was looking online and i saw stuff about infrasound and how it can cause feelings of dread or paranoia. i wonder if they're using something like that. if they're actually using this kind of tech to mess with me, how would they even hide it? would it even show up on a regular microphone?",
